# CreditStart

**Build your credit from zero — a step-by-step guide for first-time adults.**

---

## What it is

A simple web app (PWA) that helps students, recent grads,
first-time earners, and homemakers understand how to start
building credit safely — with a personalized action plan.

---

## Problem

Many people have no credit history and no clear starting
point. Existing tools assume users already have credit
cards, scores, or accounts.

---

## Solution

An 8-question onboarding quiz → personalized credit-start roadmap.

---

## Target Users (v1)

- College students
- Recent graduates
- First-job young adults
- Gig workers
- Homemakers / housewives

---

## Result Types

1. Starting From Zero
2. Thin File Beginner
3. Rejected / Unsure
4. Early Builder
5. Homemaker / Dependent Income  ← new

---

## Homemaker Notes

- May have joint account but no independent credit
- Can be added as authorized user on spouse's card
- Secured card in own name is possible
- Independent credit history matters for financial security

---

